  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK497">
<l>añcāmai yallāṟ ṟuṇaivēṇṭā veñcāmai</l>
<l>yeṇṇi yiṭattāṟ ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You will need no other aid than fearlessness, if you thoroughly reflect (on what you are to do), and select (a suitable) place for your operations.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
